datasets.name: Bronx 2010 Asians Receiving SNAP
datasets.description: Bronx census tract boundaries from the 2010 census with SNAP data. Data reflects the percentage of recipients receiving SNAP. The total should add up or close to 100%. They are NOT the percentage of the population in that census tract receiving SNAP benefits.

datasets.name: 2010 Commute Vehicles and Subway stops
datasets.description: Bronx census tract boundaries from the 2010 census with ACS data regarding the average commute time, and number of vehicles used to commute per census tract. Also, Subway infrastructure is overlayed in order to determine a relationship between car ownership and access to public transportation.
